TITLE: Episode 141 - The Cathedral in Time with Elias Dummer
DESCRIPTION: This week, we are joined by Elias Dummer. If you've ever heard the City Harmonic, you've heard this man's voice. He's a musician, an artist, a thinker, a speaker, a believer, and a fantastic content creator. With a vision of unity and beauty in the church, he's a great person to talk to about worship, our culture, and all things Christianity.
